# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:58
translate spanish hwb_s12e_aa751632:

    # "The campsite has cleared up a lot since set out this morning. It’s still pretty full, but at least it's not claustrophobic anymore."
    "El campamento se ha despejado bastante desde que salimos esta mañana. Todavía está bastante lleno, pero al menos ya no es claustrofóbico."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:60
translate spanish hwb_s12e_71baf4a4:

    # "A few campfires illuminate people that are left behind. Plus, the smoke keeps the bugs away."
    "Unas cuantas fogatas iluminan a las personas que se quedaron. Además, el humo mantiene alejados a los insectos."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:64
translate spanish hwb_s12e_d58ae674:

    # "All five of us huddle outside my RV. The goodbyes are taking a while, since Marina has to hug everyone at least twice."
    "Los cinco nos apiñamos afuera de mi casa rodante. Las despedidas están tomando tiempo, porque Marina tiene que abrazar a todos al menos dos veces."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:66
translate spanish hwb_s12e_8eb6aca1:

    # "Then she says something to reignite the conversation and the whole process starts over."
    "Luego dice algo para reavivar la conversación y todo el proceso comienza de nuevo."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:68
translate spanish hwb_s12e_fa60e2aa:

    # "Finally, I grab the door handle to signal that we’re about done. Marina automatically begins the final round of hugs."
    "Finalmente, agarro la manija de la puerta para señalar que ya casi terminamos. Marina automáticamente comienza la ronda final de abrazos."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:73
translate spanish hwb_s12e_de595dd3:

    # Marina "So, what’s next for you guys?"
    Marina "Какие у вас дальнейшие планы, ребят?"

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:75
translate spanish hwb_s12e_c3bf8e82:

    # "Maybe not."
    "Quizás no."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:77
translate spanish hwb_s12e_93d27520:

    # Mariah "Back to poring over the journal to see what we can find. Once we locate it, it’s straight off to wherever."
    Mariah "Обратно изучать дневник в надежде что-то выяснить. После того, как мы поймем где сокровище, то двинемся прямо туда."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:82
translate spanish hwb_s12e_ab15ad59:

    # "Joseph heaves a heavy sigh."
    "Joseph suelta un suspiro profundo."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:84
translate spanish hwb_s12e_f23d68cf:

    # Joseph "No rest for the weary."
    Joseph "И никакого отдыха для уставших."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:91
translate spanish hwb_s12e_0987a62f:

    # Mariah "You don’t get weary, slacker. You get motivated."
    Mariah "Не уставай, лентяй. Мотивируйся."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:95
translate spanish hwb_s12e_b63104dc:

    # Marina "Oooh. You should put that on a shirt."
    Marina "Ооооо, тебе нужно выпускать футболки с такой надписью."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:99
translate spanish hwb_s12e_e11c6025:

    # Mariah "Would you buy one?"
    Mariah "Купишь себе?"

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:104
translate spanish hwb_s12e_fe0aa0d0:

    # Tess "Nobody would."
    Tess "Никто не купит."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:108
translate spanish hwb_s12e_f65de4a5:

    # Mariah "Then no."
    Mariah "Тогда, ответ - нет."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:118
translate spanish hwb_s12e_dd57c9a7:

    # "All of us, even Mariah, laugh a little."
    "Todos nosotros, incluso Mariah, reímos un poco."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:120
translate spanish hwb_s12e_5fc86f82:

    # "Finally, Joseph puts his arm around Tess and starts to lead them away."
    "Finalmente, Joseph pasa su brazo alrededor de Tess y comienza a llevárselos."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:122
translate spanish hwb_s12e_1f192ea6:

    # Joseph "We’ll get out of your hair for the night now."
    Joseph "Пожалуй, мы перестанем вас донимать на сегодня."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:131
translate spanish hwb_s12e_05bb842e:

    # "Starting down the path, they walk towards their motorhome."
    "Bajando por el camino, caminan hacia su casa rodante."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:137
translate spanish hwb_s12e_a88fbadd:

    # Amber "Wait a sec!"
    Amber "Подождите!"

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:139
translate spanish hwb_s12e_709225a2:

    # "They freeze."
    "Se quedan paralizados."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:141
translate spanish hwb_s12e_6aeb9e62:

    # "Marina looks at me too, curious."
    "Marina también me mira, curiosa."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:145
translate spanish hwb_s12e_1f46fca4:

    # Amber "Next piece is almost definitely at Arches, in Utah."
    Amber "Следующая часть клада в парке Арчес в Юте, я уверена."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:153
translate spanish hwb_s12e_a051f39a:

    # "I hear Marina gasp, though I don’t see it."
    "Escucho a Marina jadear, aunque no lo veo."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:159
translate spanish hwb_s12e_73aade8d:

    # "Joseph and Tess both look to Mariah, their profiles barely visible from the flickering campfires in the distance."
    "Joseph y Tess miran a Mariah, sus perfiles apenas visibles por las fogatas parpadeantes a lo lejos."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:161
translate spanish hwb_s12e_dde9f050:

    # "Mariah nods stiffly."
    "Mariah asiente rígidamente."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:163
translate spanish hwb_s12e_c7c1ed22:

    # Mariah "Thanks."
    Mariah "Пасиб."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:165
translate spanish hwb_s12e_bd8c155c:

    # "It’s probably the first time she’s ever said that word."
    "Probablemente es la primera vez que dice esa palabra."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:167
translate spanish hwb_s12e_58a33d71:

    # "With a wave of her hand, she turns and they finally leave."
    "Con un movimiento de su mano, se da la vuelta y finalmente se van."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:181
translate spanish hwb_s12e_10732982:

    # "Marina and I both watch until they vanish out of sight. Then Marina squeals."
    "Marina y yo miramos hasta que desaparecen de la vista. Entonces Marina chilla."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:185
translate spanish hwb_s12e_48efb723:

    # Marina "I’m so proud of you, Amber! And shocked! That was super nice of you!"
    Marina "Я так горжусь тобой, Эмбер! Это было супер мило с твоей стороны!"

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:189
translate spanish hwb_s12e_5b43ba13:

    # Amber "Wasn’t much. This one’s pretty easy to figure out when you take the time. I probably saved them half an hour at best."
    Amber "Ничего особого. На самом деле догадаться было не трудно. Я сэкономила им от силы полчаса их времени."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:193
translate spanish hwb_s12e_b60e8bf0:

    # Marina "Still. It’s the thought that counts!"
    Marina "Но все же, это считается!"

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:197
translate spanish hwb_s12e_6dc0cab9:

    # Marina "Why’d you do it, though?"
    Marina "Но почему ты так поступила?"

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:201
translate spanish hwb_s12e_dfd7f3ee:

    # Amber "Someone’s gotta take care of them, after all."
    Amber "Кто-то же должен о них позаботиться."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:203
translate spanish hwb_s12e_43ed8ea3:

    # "I look away, pretending to scratch an itch on my cheek."
    "Desvío la mirada, fingiendo rascarme una picazón en la mejilla."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:207
translate spanish hwb_s12e_af6f2b28:

    # Amber "They're not {i}that{/i} bad."
    Amber "Они {i}не на столько{/i} плохи."

# game/script/hwb_s12e.rpy:58
translate spanish hwb_s12e_ee7dd814:

    # "The campsite has cleared up a lot since we set out this morning. It’s still pretty full, but at least it's not claustrophobic anymore."
    "El campamento se ha despejado bastante desde que salimos esta mañana. Todavía está bastante lleno, pero al menos ya no es claustrofóbico."

